title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Nov 5 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Nov 5 2022
description:
Lee Zeldin joins Clay and Buck to talk about what it will take for NY to elect its first GOP governor since 1994. A former NY police officer calls to discuss the governor's race. Jennifer-Ruth Green, Indiana congressional candidate and Air Force veteran joins C&B. Buck recommends Netflix's All Quiet on the Western Front.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
